&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;69%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Assess the condition of the historic environment, including actioning measures for monitoring, protection and discharge of legal responsibilities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
