&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Prepare, appraise, lead or provide advice on plans for the management of change of heritage assets and areas, and strategies for managing their loss, their protection, enhancement or regeneration, including preparation, appraisal and management of statutory consents and legal responsibilities, including supporting statements, conditions, appeals and enforcement/prosecution.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;30%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K1&lt;span&gt; K2 K3 K4 K5 K6 K7 K13 K15 K17 K18 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;S1&lt;span&gt; S2 S3 S4 S5 S7 S8 S9 S13 S14 S15 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;B1&lt;span&gt; B2 B5 B6 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
