&lt;p&gt;B1&lt;span&gt; B2 B5 B6 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;69%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Provide advice on or assess sustainability in the historic environment. For buildings, it includes assessment of building performance and potential for retrofitting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;30%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K1&lt;span&gt; K2 K4 K7 K15 K17 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;S1&lt;span&gt; S2 S3 S4 S13 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;B1&lt;span&gt; B2 B5 B6 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
